    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 6 (Spell Level 3)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 20 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 8 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 21</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, F, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique was created in the Hidden Village of Steel, and is a particularly useful wartime skill that allows you to quickly create weaponry. You shape metal, allowing you to create simple, standard quality weapons. You make a Craft (Mechanical) check to craft the weapon(s), and halve the time required to do so. The weapons cannot be mastercrafted after being created.</p>\n\n\n\n",
